ses?f%5B0%5D=field_decision_method%3A145">Voting</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-decision-voting-type field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">If voting...:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_decision_voting_type%3A149">Super-Majoritarian Voting (i.e. threshold more than 50%+1)</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-targeted-audience field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Targeted Audience :&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_targeted_audience%3A151">General Public</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_targeted_audience%3A152">Elected Public Official</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-audience-comm-method field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Method of Communication with Audience:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_audience_comm_method%3A158">Policy Recommendations</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_audience_comm_method%3A159">Public Hearings/Meetings</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="collapsible group-organizers field-group-div speed-fast effect-none">
